You wanna go upstairs?

807
00:42:55.921 --> 00:42:57.141
Hmm?

808
00:42:58.358 --> 00:43:00.268
Come on. bug!

809
00:43:00.403 --> 00:43:04.023
Let's go read
the "Cromawhatsit."

810
00:43:04.146 --> 00:43:05.406
