It's The Cromenockle.

811
00:43:05.539 --> 00:43:07.189
Oh. yeah. sure.

812
00:43:07.323 --> 00:43:09.203
That's what I said -
the "Cromawhatsit."

813
00:43:09.325 --> 00:43:11.935
Come on. All right.
Just take it slow.

814
00:43:12.067 --> 00:43:14.237
You're good.

815
00:43:14.374 --> 00:43:16.814
Yeah. You got this.

816
00:43:20.162 --> 00:43:21.252
